<%- include('../partials/header', { title: 'Buat Tiket Baru' }) %>

<style>
    /*
    ============================================
    --- NEW TICKET PAGE STYLING ---
    ============================================
    */
    .page-header {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .page-header h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 15px;
    }
    .page-header h1 i {
        background: var(--gradient-primary);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .page-header p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        max-width: 600px;
    }
    
    .ticket-form-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .form-main-card {
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
        padding: 2.5rem;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }
    
    /* Form Styling */
    .form-group label {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--color-text-dark);
    }
    .form-group .form-control {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
        background-color: var(--color-bg-light);
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .form-group .form-control:focus {
        background-color: white;
        border-color: var(--color-primary-start);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(74, 0, 224, 0.15);
        outline: none;
    }
    .form-group textarea.form-control {
        min-height: 150px;
        resize: vertical;
    }

    /* Custom File Input */
    .form-group input[type="file"] {
        background-color: white;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .form-group input[type="file"]::file-selector-button {
        padding: 12px 18px;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
        border: none;
        background: var(--gradient-primary);
        color: white;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-right: 1rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .form-group input[type="file"]::file-selector-button:hover {
        opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .form-group small {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
    }

    .btn-submit {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 16px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    /* --- Sidebar Tips Card --- */
    .sidebar-tips-card {
        background-color: #eef3ff;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
        padding: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-primary-start);
    }
    .sidebar-tips-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--color-text-dark);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
    }
    .sidebar-tips-card h3 i {
        color: var(--color-primary-start);
    }
    .sidebar-tips-card ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
    }
    .sidebar-tips-card li {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--color-text-dark);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .sidebar-tips-card li i {
        color: var(--color-success);
        margin-top: 4px;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 992px) {
        .ticket-form-layout {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>

<div class="container" style="padding-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 3rem;">
    <div class="page-header">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i> Buat Tiket Bantuan Baru</h1>
        <p>Jelaskan masalah Anda secara rinci agar tim kami dapat membantu lebih cepat dan akurat.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ticket-form-layout">
        <div class="form-main-card">
            <form action="/dashboard/tickets/new" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="subject">Subjek</label>
                    <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" class="form-control" required placeholder="Contoh: Tidak bisa mengakses DNS Manager">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="department">Departemen</label>
                    <select id="department" name="department" class="form-control" required>
                        <option value="Teknis">Dukungan Teknis</option>
                        <option value="Billing">Penagihan (Billing)</option>
                        <option value="Lainnya">Lainnya</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="message">Pesan</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" class="form-control" rows="8" required placeholder="Jelaskan kendala Anda di sini..."></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="attachment">Lampirkan Screenshot (Opsional)</label>
                    <input type="file" name="attachment" id="attachment" class="form-control" accept="image/png, image/jpeg, image/gif">
                    <small>Format yang diizinkan: JPG, PNG, GIF. Ukuran maksimal 2MB.</small>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-submit">Kirim Tiket</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-tips-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Tips Mengisi Tiket</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                    <div><strong>Subjek yang Jelas.</strong> Gunakan subjek yang singkat dan deskriptif.</div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                    <div><strong>Jelaskan Kronologi.</strong> Ceritakan langkah-langkah yang Anda lakukan sebelum masalah terjadi.</div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                    <div><strong>Sertakan Detail.</strong> Cantumkan nama domain, layanan, atau ID faktur yang terkait.</div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                    <div><strong>Pesan Error.</strong> Jika ada pesan error, salin dan tempel pesan tersebut secara lengkap.</div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                    <div><strong>Gunakan Screenshot.</strong> Sebuah gambar bisa menjelaskan lebih dari seribu kata.</div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>